line_1: Whether thro' wimplin worms thou jink,
line_2: O thou, my MUSE! guid, auld SCOTCH DRINK!

line_1: Whether thro' wimplin worms thou jink,
line_2: Or, richly brown, ream owre the brink,

line_1: Whether thro' wimplin worms thou jink,
line_2: Inspire me, till I lisp an' wink,

line_1: Our billie's gien us a' a jink,
line_2: A' Ye wha live by sowps o' drink,

line_1: Our billie's gien us a' a jink,
line_2: A' ye wha live by crambo-clink,

line_1: Our billie's gien us a' a jink,
line_2: A' ye wha live and never think,
